# SceneParser raw-XML capture corpus — contains other players' chatter; never commit
corpus/

# Local harnesses (tmp-scene-harness = the SceneParser capturer regression
# suite, tmp-scroll-repro = the B171/B172 scroll simulation). Kept OUT of the
# repo on purpose: the scene harness embeds verbatim corpus lines with real
# player names (Sekmeht, 2026-06-12 — same privacy stance as corpus/). They
# live machine-local; pitfalls #81/#35.4 document how to rebuild them.
tmp-*/

